Map by kata$ (ESP)

Ba_jail_laser_v3 has a similar structure and elements of the ba_jail_electric. I hope you will like it :)

 - This map was made for 32 players max.
 - The custom materials are packed in the BSP File.
 - There is a Roulette Room, if you press the button on the center of the spec room you will be the next who will do a roulette when your equip member die.

THX FOR PLAYING
